{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-sermons-list-js","path":"/en/sermons/page/57","result":{"pageContext":{"pagination":{"total":1038,"current":57},"lang":"en","nodes":[{"id":"22316","title":"The Media Mind - Part 2","imageWithFallback":{"url":"https://s.audioverse.org/english/gallery/persons/_/50/50/Ritsma-Scott2020.jpg"},"persons":[{"name":"Scott Ritsema"}],"duration":5066.1,"recordingDate":"2020-07-30T15:30:00.000Z","audioFiles":[{"url":"https://www.audioverse.org/english/download/dl/78987/2020/08/22316/20200730-1530-22316-748cd2f570dc3b8cba0fd275c509570a-96k.mp3"},{"url":"https://www.audioverse.org/english/download/dl/78988/2020/08/22316/20200730-1530-22316-748cd2f570dc3b8cba0fd275c509570a-48k.mp3"},{"url":"https://www.audioverse.org/english/download/dl/78989/2020/08/22316/20200730-1530-22316-748cd2f570dc3b8cba0fd275c509570a-16k.mp3"}],"description":"<p>Hollywood, popular music, video gaming, spectator sports, and endless social media are saturating the lives of God&rsquo;s professed people. But what does the latest science say about the mind-altering effects of 21st century media? And what is the spiritual agenda in the entertainment and advertising industries?&nbsp; Join Scott for 2 sessions on this crucial topic &ndash; 1) a review of Media on the Brain, 2) updates from the new seminar, The Media Mind.</p>"},{"id":"22315","title":"Media on the Brain - Part 1","imageWithFallback":{"url":"https://s.audioverse.org/english/gallery/persons/_/50/50/Ritsma-Scott2020.jpg"},"persons":[{"name":"Scott Ritsema"}],"duration":5120.5,"recordingDate":"2020-07-30T10:45:00.000Z","audioFiles":[{"url":"https://www.audioverse.org/english/download/dl/78990/2020/08/22315/20200730-1045-22315-c3002404af446963dfed2bd31e4dcbfa-96k.mp3"},{"url":"https://www.audioverse.org/english/download/dl/78991/2020/08/22315/20200730-1045-22315-c3002404af446963dfed2bd31e4dcbfa-48k.mp3"},{"url":"https://www.audioverse.org/english/download/dl/78992/2020/08/22315/20200730-1045-22315-c3002404af446963dfed2bd31e4dcbfa-16k.mp3"}],"description":"<p>Hollywood, popular music, video gaming, spectator sports, and endless social media are saturating the lives of God&rsquo;s professed people. But what does the latest science say about the mind-altering effects of 21st century media? And what is the spiritual agenda in the entertainment and advertising industries?&nbsp; Join Scott for 2 sessions on this crucial topic &ndash; 1) a review of Media on the Brain, 2) updates from the new seminar, The Media Mind.</p>"},{"id":"22313","title":"Right Time, Right Place, Right Message","imageWithFallback":{"url":"https://s.audioverse.org/english/gallery/persons/_/50/50/walton_lewis1.jpg"},"persons":[{"name":"Lewis Walton"}],"duration":4115.8,"recordingDate":"2020-07-31T10:45:00.000Z","audioFiles":[{"url":"https://www.audioverse.org/english/download/dl/78973/2020/08/22313/20200731-1045-22313-be41655015cca5c9eeb4105f7658a9c4-96k.mp3"},{"url":"https://www.audioverse.org/english/download/dl/78974/2020/08/22313/20200731-1045-22313-be41655015cca5c9eeb4105f7658a9c4-48k.mp3"},{"url":"https://www.audioverse.org/english/download/dl/78975/2020/08/22313/20200731-1045-22313-be41655015cca5c9eeb4105f7658a9c4-16k.mp3"}],"description":"<p>The Three Angel&rsquo;s Messages are the very core of what we are commissioned to proclaim.&nbsp; In 9 powerful verses, Revelation 14 describes the people and the message to be shared with an end-time world.&nbsp; This seminar will portray the mission of Seventh-day Adventists as heaven sees it.</p>"},{"id":"22314","title":"God's Wrath in Revelation","imageWithFallback":{"url":"https://s.audioverse.org/english/gallery/persons/_/50/50/grabiner_steven2.jpg"},"persons":[{"name":"Steven Grabiner"}],"duration":4260.2,"recordingDate":"2020-07-31T15:30:00.000Z","audioFiles":[{"url":"https://www.audioverse.org/english/download/dl/78978/2020/08/22314/20200731-1530-22314-f83744c77b821d4fc606c58b5113690d-96k.mp3"},{"url":"https://www.audioverse.org/english/download/d